st visionaries=E2=80=94Leonardo da Vinci, Albert Einstein and Steve Jobs, t=
o name a few=E2=80=94author Walter Isaacson explored the traits and practic=
es creative geniuses have in common and uncovered how to glean lessons from=
 the past to impact the future.</em></p>
