p;Isaacson reflected on the recovery efforts in New Orleans after Hurricane=
 Katrina. =E2=80=9CAt a certain point, we said, =E2=80=98The question is no=
t: How do we rebuild the city we had? But the question is: How do we build =
the city we want to have?=E2=80=99=E2=80=9D He encouraged members to apply =
this to their own companies and ask, =E2=80=9CHow are we going not just to =
restore our company but build our company new in a different way and use th=
is crisis as an opportunity?=E2=80=9D</li>
</ul>

