ees and =E2=80=9Cusing all parts of our skills=E2=80=94left brain, right
=
brain, heart and soul=E2=80=9D=E2=80=94are the ways businesses can create =
=E2=80=9Cirrational performance=E2=80=9D in uncertain times.</li>
=09<li>=
<strong>Unleashing human magic ::</strong>&nbsp;As a leader, he said, =
=E2=80=9CDefining what to do is usually relatively easy, defining how to do=
 it is a bit harder, and it=E2=80=99s doing it that=E2=80=99s the hard part=
.=E2=80=9D To effectively do what must be done, you must mobilize your orga=
nization by focusing on =E2=80=9Cunleashing human magic=E2=80=9D=E2=80=
=94helping connect what drives the individuals within your company with the=
 organization=E2=80=99s purpose. Focus on building authentic human connecti=
ons, creating a growth environment and pushing decision-making down in the =
organization as much as possible.</li>
