=09=09<li><strong>How are you taking care of yourself?&nbsp;<=
/strong>This crisis requires you to be the best leader you can be. Are you =
spending enough time thinking about how you want to lead and how you want t=
o be remembered? Are you taking care of yourself physically, mentally and s=
piritually?&nbsp;</li>
=09=09<li><strong>How are your team members taking=
 care of themselves?&nbsp;</strong>Joly encouraged members to ask the above=
 questions to each person on their teams. =E2=80=9CWe all need to get to kn=
ow the people around us on a much deeper level than we ever have.=E2=80=
=9D</li>
=09=09<li><strong>What changes are impacting us?&nbsp;</strong>O=
