<ul>
=09<li><strong>Link technology to value ::&n=
bsp;</strong>Mauborgne argued that there=E2=80=99s a remarkable confusion b=
etween technological innovation and value innovation. =E2=80=9CTechnology i=
nnovation doesn=E2=80=99t create new markets; it only creates new markets w=
hen it=E2=80=99s applied to the value consumers use.=E2=80=9D Technology of=
ten gets pushed first without considering if it=E2=80=99s strategically pri=
ced for the market, if it=E2=80=99s simple and easy to use, or if it improv=
es users=E2=80=99 lives. =E2=80=9CHow do you link technology to value? The =
companies that create blue oceans always start with the value to the market=
 and work backward from there.=E2=80=9D</li>
=09<li><strong>Six ways to r=
econstruct markets ::&nbsp;</strong>Companies tend to innovate in the same =
way as their competitors because they benchmark against each other. As an a=
lternative, Mauborgne shared six ways to reshape market boundaries and appl=
y blue-ocean thinking.&nbsp;
=09<ul>
=09=09<li><strong>Across industrie=
s:&nbsp;</strong>Look across alternative industries instead of at the compe=
tition within your own industry.&nbsp;</li>
=09=09<li><strong>Across stra=
tegic groups:&nbsp;</strong>Look across strategic groups. =E2=80=9CInstead =
of focusing on a strategic group within an industry, why do people trade up=
 and down between two strategic groups?=E2=80=9D</li>
=09=09<li><strong>B=
uyer group:&nbsp;</strong>What value would you see if you switched the buye=
r group?</li>
=09=09<li><strong>Complementary products and services:</str=
ong>&nbsp;=E2=80=9CWe tend to focus on only one product or service.=
=E2=80=9D Where are there complementary products and services?</li>
=09=
=09<li><strong>Functional and emotional:&nbsp;</strong>Can you take a funct=
ional product and make it emotional, or vice versa? Can you switch those tw=
o within an industry?</li>
=09=09<li><strong>Time:&nbsp;</strong>Can you =
understand the irreversible trends in your industry, seeing analogous indus=
tries that have gone through those trends, and then identify how you can ch=
ange value today to meet that trend as it develops.</li>
=09</ul>
